imageDescription: A simple image that represents this song is a vibrant, blooming flower surrounded by fluttering butterflies. The flower symbolizes love and the butterflies represent the feeling of joy and freedom. The image captures the energetic and carefree essence of the song, with the colorful beauty of the flowers and the graceful movement of the butterflies.
